SELECT user_id, CONCAT(UPPER(LEFT(name,1)),LOWER(RIGHT(name,LEN(name)-1))) AS name
FROM Users
ORDER BY user_id

Input
Users =
| user_id | name  |
| ------- | ----- |
| 1       | aLice |
| 2       | bOB   |
Output
| user_id | name  |
| ------- | ----- |
| 1       | Alice |
| 2       | Bob   |
Expected
| user_id | name  |
| ------- | ----- |
| 1       | Alice |
| 2       | Bob   |
